data.description: Indulge in this cozy 2600 sq. ft. ranch-style home nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac with 3 beds, 3.5 baths and many upgrades, it's an entertainer's haven.  Renovated kitchen w/ JennAir appliances and an outdoor courtyard. Sip wine at the custom bar, and unwind on the large screened porch with an artificial turf fenced backyard to nature preserve. Updated master suite offers a serene retreat with spa-like bathroom. Guests enjoy ensuite accommodations on the opposite end. This “One of a Kind” home in Hampton Lake boasts ample ground-level storage, tankless water heater, and plantation shutters throughout. A must see!
